snippet.title: How Will ChatGPT Impact Software Developers with Sten Hougaard
snippet.description:
Welcome to my part of the GOTO Night event, where I dive into how software developers can incorporate ChatGPT into their daily work. Join me as I share insights and reflections from the event held in May 2023 at Trifork's venue on Sankt Knuds Torv, in Aarhus, Denmark.

üé• Watch the recording of my session as I explore the potential of ChatGPT, powered by OpenAI, to revolutionize programming practices.

üìÖ Event details: https://gotopia.tech/events/146/chatGPT-impact-on-programming

üìΩÔ∏è In this video, you'll find my presentation on how ChatGPT enhances productivity, assists with code reviews, and its implications for the future of software development. Feel free to check out my slides too: https://slides.com/stenhougaard/how-will-chatgpt-impact-software-developers

Whether you attended the GOTO Night event or not, this recap is your chance to get valuable insights on the impact of AI in programming. Let's discuss and shape the future of software development together!

snippet.title: Brusebadsboller - bagning
snippet.description:
Brusebadsboller er en simpel opskrift og metode til at lave (morgen)boller som er nemme at lave og smager godt.

Min opskrift er noget jeg har eksperimenteret mig frem til, og du kan tilpasse ingredienserne s√• de passer din smag:

Giver ca. 8 boller
1) 400 g mel (jeg bruge 1/3 groftmel og resten hvedemel)
2) 4 deciliter koldt vand
3) 1 tsk salt
4) 1 tsk sukker
5) Lidt g√¶r - f.eks. 12 gram
6) Solsikke kerner

Man opl√∏ser g√¶r i vandet, og blander derefter resten af ingredienserne i. Det skal ikke √¶ltes med h√¶nderne og det er en ret kl√¶brig dej.

Stil det i k√∏leskabet og n√•r du skal lave dem tager du bare det du skal bruge og l√¶gger p√• en br√¶ddepande og stiller dejen tilbage i k√∏leskabet. Det skulle man efter sigende kunne g√∏re i 5 dage.

Jeg pynter mine boller med birkes.

BAGNING:
Varm ovnen til f.eks. 250 grader varmluft
S√¶t bollerne ind og giv dem 5 minutter 
Skrue ned til 210 grader

S√• kan du tage et bad p√• ca. 15 minutter og dine Brusebadsboller er klar til at spise! God appetit!

snippet.title: Instant browser based React Native testing
snippet.description:
I show how you using only a browser can do instant React native testing, both in iOS an Android. The app is coded in ES2015 JavaScript using React Native and requires no compiling or building. The code runs and updates as you type, and your can see the result in a free app found at https://expo.io/ which is available for both iOS and Android.

The example app can be seen here: https://snack.expo.io/Sk6H4ayqb

 snack.expo.io
 react-native-training.github.io/react-native-elements/
